						<p>On a broken slab set up in front of the <hi rend="italic">chāvaḍi.</hi></p>						

						<p>Circa 12th century.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land to the god Kēśava by Chāvuṇḍa-gāvuṇḍa and Rēvagāvuṇḍa. The epigraph is damaged.</p>						

